{"tid":1875134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府：宜家有人免費派口罩 所以根本唔洗管制口罩價格","createTime":"2020-02-11T14:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T17:08:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6963680ab68812f0b3f53291d1fe839bb601d814","tid":1875134,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員葉劉淑儀日前出席電台節目時透露，政府正研究立法規管，包括口罩等防疫物品供應，更預告數星期內會有消息。怎料政府晚上出稿否認，指在口罩供應緊絀下，硬性規管價格及供應只會適得其反。《政情》向葉劉淑儀查詢，她強調政府一直研究規管口罩，直至政府出稿才知不會落實。<br />\n<br />\n月初不少政黨都建議透過法例管制口罩價格，不過，有政黨都認為，當時農曆新年假期確實有個別商店抬價，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過近日大多商店都以成本價出售，甚至是免費派發，認同口罩問題的根源是量而不是價</span></span></strong>。而參考其他地方推價格規管，本身是口罩生產國，認為香港未必有條件用此辣招。<br />\n<br />\n【政情】立法規管口罩銷售　葉劉放風終撲空<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=380251&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380251%26refer%3DShare&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=436a2411\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380251%26refer%3DShare&h=88bd7eda\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=380251&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"45005784691531e2dffdafc69ae85053cc45cd8e","tid":1875134,"uid":726,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T14:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過近日大多商店都以成本價出售，甚至是免費派發</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母應該捉晒你班傻鳩去排口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b637b8aa26920aab19c2d22bbb45f22e0e0d793","tid":1875134,"uid":128117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NuQzdKc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNuQzdKc.gif&h=7069daea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59eb9cdbe4d2719c8f056ab65bb29afff156fb38","tid":1875134,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:05:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f69329c8771d180359924d6c85cf15d6352f74b6","tid":1875134,"uid":73600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T17:08:12.000Z","msg":"她強調政府一直研究規管口罩，直至政府出稿才知不會落實。<br />\n<br />\n研究啲唔會落實既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}